											<p>Any querys? Contact 24/7</p>
											<h6>
												<b>
													<span class="text-900">Call Us:</span>
													<span class="phone-number"><span t-out="res_company.phone"/></span>
												</b>
											</h6>
											<p>
												<span t-out="res_company.street"/>,<br/>
